flavor_text_entries.gold:
They say that it
will appear before
kindhearted, car­ ing people and
shower them with
happiness.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It grows dispirit­
ed if it is not
with kind people. It can float in
midair without
moving its wings.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
Although it does
not flap its wings
very much, it can stay up in the air
as it tags along
after its trainer.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
TOGETIC is said to be a POKéMON that
brings good fortune. When the POKéMON
spots someone who is pure of heart, it is said to appear and share its
happiness with that person.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
No records exist of Togetic being seen in the wilds. Rumors
abound that it evolves under the loving care of a trusted human
companion, upon whom the Pokémon then bestows great joy.
